---
title: Pork Banh Mi-Style Bowls with Pickled Carrots and Radishes
description: We've taken the traditional banh mi sandwich and turned it on its head! This quick and tasty meal has everything you love about the original, packed into a satisfying dinner with fluffy jasmine rice. Spicy mayo, pickled veggies and saucy pork all come together for a Vietnamese-inspired party in a bowl!
